      "raw_text": "Large blocks of Snowstorm came\non the market shortly after the\nopening of trading this morning\nand broke the price materially. The\nquantity of stock apparently for\nsale would indicate lower prices to.\nwards the end of the week There\nis evidence that the Federal com\npany is getting ready to take on\nsome new properties in the Occur\nd'Alenes. The tariff bill in it's pres\nent form is apparently eminently\nsatisfactory to lead miners of this\ndistrict, as far as it affects lead\n\n\nand the indications are that cap\nital is going to be DESTROYS of en-\ntering the lead field in the near\nfuture. The Federal company needs\none or two new producers to pay"
